Implementation:

board = contains grid plus timer plus labels, has render function

grid = 9x9 filled with nils on init

square = single box with bomb or number of bombs it touches, has a mark and a status
      status: bomb or no bomb ==> set on game initialize
      has_bomb: boolean
      marks: unmarked, marked as bomb, checked safe(shows number), detonated bomb (player loses) ==> changed on each user input

(timer) 

player = input functions to get move

